import React from 'react'
import {Navbar,Nav,NavDropdown, Container } from 'react-bootstrap'

const Header = () => {
    return (
        <header dir="rtl">
            <Navbar bg="light" expand="lg">
                <Container>
                  <Navbar.Brand href="#home">תכשיטי תהילה</Navbar.Brand>
                 <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
                 <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
                   <Nav className="me-auto">
                        <Nav.Link href="#home">דף הבית</Nav.Link>
                       <Nav.Link href="#link">לינק</Nav.Link>
                        <NavDropdown title="תכשיטים" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
                         <NavDropdown.Item className="rtl" href="#action/3.1">טבעות</NavDropdown.Item>
                          <NavDropdown.Item className="rtl" href="#action/3.2">עגילים</NavDropdown.Item>
                         <NavDropdown.Item className="rtl" href="#action/3.3">שרשראות</NavDropdown.Item>
                         <NavDropdown.Item className="rtl" href="#action/3.4">שעונים</NavDropdown.Item>
                          <NavDropdown.Divider />
                          <NavDropdown.Item className="rtl" href="#action/3.5">לינק מופרד</NavDropdown.Item>
                    </NavDropdown>
                   </Nav>
                  </Navbar.Collapse>
                 </Container>
            </Navbar>
        </header>
    )
}

export default Header
